<TEXT>
CREDIT Lyonnais, the French bank which owns Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer, said that
it had no immediate plans to sell the Hollywood film studio following an
announcement by Mr William Koch that he plans to make an offer for the
company, writes Karen Zagor in New York.
