FT  29 SEP 93 / UK Company News: Allied London Props jumps to Pounds 6.8m
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Allied London Properties, the property investor and developer, lifted
pre-tax profits from Pounds 1.49m to Pounds 6.8m in the year to June 30.
Net rental income rose from Pounds 17.1m to Pounds 18.7m. Trading profits
amounted to Pounds 438,000 (Pounds 562,000) and other income totalled Pounds
