reflected a reduction in the value of the group's housebuilding assets.
An unchanged final dividend of 2.455p is recommended to maintain the total
at 3.53p. Earnings per share worked through at 5p against losses of 1.5p.
Net asset value per share stood at 85p at June 30 against 90p a year
earlier. Fully diluted, the figure was 95p (100p). At the year end the
property portfolio was valued at Pounds 180m.
