THE SMALLER Companies Investment Trust is proposing its second substantial
fund raising exercise in five months.
The trust, managed by Abtrust Fund Managers, is attempting to raise some
Pounds 23.8m, net of expenses, through a conditional plac-ing of C shares at
135p apiece.
